00:14:48,612 --> 00:14:51,156
He had words with 
Della and Derek that night.

255
00:14:51,156 --> 00:14:53,915
Well, her throat being cut
says it was more personal than that.

256
00:14:53,915 --> 00:14:56,147
She dissed him in front of his crew.

257
00:14:56,147 --> 00:14:58,321
That's personal 
to these mugwumps.

258
00:14:58,582 --> 00:15:00,607
J.T. Simms' juvie records.

