264
00:15:13,388 --> 00:15:15,294
We'll follow up on Tyra.

265
00:15:15,294 --> 00:15:16,931
Simms is the better bet.

266
00:15:16,931 --> 00:15:18,398
Run them both down.

267
00:15:18,398 --> 00:15:21,213
Check on Derek's friend, Joe,
while you're at it.

268
00:15:23,418 --> 00:15:25,348
Let's hit the Badlands.

269
00:15:34,415 --> 00:15:35,897
We understand the 
night of the murders,

270
00:15:35,897 --> 00:15:37,890
you and Della were arguing.

271
00:15:38,937 --> 00:15:39,991
No, I don't think so.

272
00:15:39,991 --> 00:15:42,462
Della's daughter says it was over
